Package com.datamelt.rules.reader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvReader
    CsvReader class is used to run the business rule engine against data from a CSV file.
    DatabaseReader
    DatabaseReader class is used to run the business rule engine against data from a MySql database.
    SimpleReader
    SimpleReader class is used to run the business rule engine using a rule zip file against a simple set of data.
    TextFileReader
    TextFileReader class is used to run the business rule engine against data from a fixed length ASCII file.
